headline: Expeditors Appoints New CEO as Jeffrey S. Musser Announces Retirement
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., February 19, 2025--Expeditors International of Washington, Inc. (NYSE:EXPD) today announced that Jeffrey S. Musser, President and Chief Executive Officer, plans to retire, effective March 31, 2025. The Company also announced that the Board of Directors has unanimously elected Daniel R.
